Package: perfsonar-core
Architecture: all
Depends: perfsonar-testpoint, esmond, ${misc:Depends}
Description: perfSONAR core metapackage - beta
 perfSONAR combines a number of measurement tools and services.
 .
 perfSONAR core metapackage installs bwctl and owamp server
 along with tools to publish the location of these services to the
 perfSONAR-PS Simple Lookup Service, run regular tests and
 a Measurement Archive for storing results.
 .
 This type of installation also contains the bwctl, owamp and ndt
 command-line clients so that you may run one-time tests to
 other servers.
 .
 This package is currently a beta release.

Package: perfsonar-centralmanagement
Architecture: all
Depends: perfsonar-meshconfig-jsonbuilder, perfsonar-meshconfig-guiagent,
 perfsonar-lsregistrationdaemon, maddash, esmond, ${misc:Depends}
Description: perfSONAR central management metapackage - beta
 perfSONAR combines a number of measurement tools and services.
 .
 perfSONAR central metapackage installs Mesh configuration tools,
 MaDDash framework for scheduling service checks and displaying results,
 and a Measurement Archive for storing results.
 .
 This package is currently a beta release.
